hadiths[145]{hadithnumber,text}:
4159,"Hazrat umr bin Abi Salma (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke zere parwarish ladka tha aur (khaney ke doran) mera haath plate mein her taraf ghoomtaa tha, (ye harkat dekh kar) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey farmaya : ''Allah ka naam lekar apney daain haath ke sath apney samney se khaao.'' muttafaq aleh."
4160,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''be-shak shetan us khaney ko , jis par Allah ka naam na liya jaey, khana halal samajhta hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
4161,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab aadmi apney ghar mein dakhil hota hai aur wo apney dakhley ke waqt aur khana khaney ke waqt Allah ka zikr karta hai to shetan kehta hai, tumharey liye na to raat guzarney ke liye koi jagah hai aur na Sham ka khana , aur jab aadmi dakhil hota hai aur wo apney dakhley ke waqt Allah ka zikr nahin karta to shetan (apney sathiyon sey) kehta hai, tum ne raat guzarney ki jagah pa li , aur jab wo khana khatey waqt Allah ka naam nahin leta to wo kehta hai : tum ne raat guzarney ki jagah pa li aur Sham ka khana bhi pa liya.'' rawahu Muslim."
4162,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi khaye to wo apney daain haath ke sath khaye aur jab piye to daain haath se piye.'' rawahu Muslim."
4163,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se koi shakhs bhi apney baeyn haath se na khaye aur na uskey sath piye, kyonkey shetan apney baeyn haath ke sath khata peeta hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
4164,"Hazrat Kab bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) teen ungliyon ke sath khaya kartey they, aur aap haath saaf karney se pehley unhen chaat liya kartey they. rawahu Muslim."
4165,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ungliyan aur plate chaatney ka hukm diya aur farmaya : ''tum nahin jantey ke (khaney ke) kis hissey mein barkat hai.'' rawahu Muslim.
4166,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi khana khaye to wo chaatney ya chataaney se pehley apna haath saaf na karey.'' muttafaq aleh.
4167,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''shetan tumharey her mamley mein , yahan tak ke khaney ke waqt bhi hazir hota hai, jab tum mein se kisi se luqma gir jaey to wo usey saaf karkey kha ley aur usey shetan ke liye na chodey, aur jab farigh ho jaey to apni ungliyan chaat ley kyonkey wo nahin janta ke uskey khaney ke kis hissey mein barkat ho.'' rawahu Muslim."
4168,"Hazrat Abu Juhaifa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main tek laga kar nahin khata.'' Bukhari."
4169,Hazrat Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne na mez par rakh kar khaya aur na tashtari mein khana khaya aur na hi chapaati khai. Qatada se puchha gaya : wo kis chiz par khana khaya kartey they? unhoney farmaya : dastar khuwan par. Bukhari.
4170,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main nahin janta ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne puri zindagi maide ki roti aur Salim bhuni hui bakri dekhi (yani khai) ho. Bukhari."
4171,"Hazrat Sehal bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne , jab se Allah ne unhen Nabi banakar bheja zindagi bhar na maide ki roti dekhi aur na chhalni, un se puchha gaya, tum phir bin-chhaney jau kaisey khatey they? unhoney kaha : ham uska aataa banatey aur phunk maartay jo chiz udni hoti wo ud jati , aur jo baqi reh jata ham usey goondh kar roti banatey aur usey kha letey they. Bukhari ."
4172,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kabhi kisi khaney mein aeb nahin nikala , agar aapney usey pasand kiya to kha liya aur agar napasand kiya to usey chhod diya. muttafaq aleh."
4173,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik aadmi bahut ziyada khaya karta tha, jab wo musalman ho gaya to kam khaney laga , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se uska zikr kiya gaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''momin eik aant mein khata hai jabkey kafir saat aanton mein khata hai.'' Bukhari."
4174,"Hazrat Imam Muslim ne Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kiya hai aur ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se sirf musnad riwayat hai, rawahu Muslim rawahu Muslim."
4175,"Hazrat Imam Muslim ne Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kiya hai aur ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se sirf musnad riwayat hai, rawahu Muslim rawahu Muslim."
4176,"Aur sahih Muslim ki dusri riwayat jo ke Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, is mein hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke yahan eik kafir shakhs mehman thehra. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik bakri ke mutalliq farmaya to uska doodh dhoya gaya, usney uska sara doodh pi liya , phir dusri ka doodh dhoya gaya to usney wo bhi pi liya , phir eik aur ka doodh dhoya gaya, usney usey bhi pi liya , yahan tak ke usney saat bakriyon ka doodh pi liya , phir agley roz usney Islam qubul kar liya , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uskey liye eik bakri ke mutalliq hukm farmaya , uska doodh dhoya gaya usney uska doodh pi liya , phir dusri ke mutalliq hukm diya gaya to wo dusri ka sara doodh na pi saka , to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''momin eik aant mein peeta hai jabkey kafir saat aanton mein peeta hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
4177,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''do (aadmiyon) ka khana teen ke liye kafi hota hai jabkey teen ka khana chaar ke liye kafi hota hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
4178,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''eik aadmi ka khana do ke liye, do ka khana chaar ke liye aur chaar ka khana aath ke liye kafi hota hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
4179,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''talbeena (jo ka daliya) dil ke mareez ke liye rahat bakhsh aur gham ko halka karney wala hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
4180,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik darzi ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko khaney par bulaya jo ke usney (khususi taur par) tayyar kya tha, main bhi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath gaya, usney jau ki roti aur shorbaa peshe-khidmat kiya jis mein kaddu aur khushk kiye huey gosht ke tukdey they, maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko plate ke kinaron mein kaddu talash kartey huey dekha, chunanche main us roz se kaddu pasand karta hun. muttafaq aleh."
4181,"Hazrat Amr bin Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke bakri ki dasti aap ke haath mein hai aur aap us se kaat kar tanaawul farma rahey hain. itney mein aap ko Namaz ke liye aawaz di gaee to aapney us (dasti) ko aur us chhuri ko jiskey sath aap kaat rahey they rakh diya, phir khadey huey aur Namaz padhi, aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne (naya) wuzu nahin farmaya. muttafaq aleh."
4182,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) meethi chizen aur shehad pasand farmaya kartey they. muttafaq aleh."
4183,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney ehale-khana se salan talab farmaya to unhoney arz kiya, hamarey paas to sirf sirka hai, aapney usey mangaayaa aur uskey sath khana khaney lagey , aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farma rahey they : ''sirka behtareen salan hai, sirka behtareen salan hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
4184,"Hazrat Saeed bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''khanbi man (bani Israel ke man aur salwaa) ki noa (qism) mein se hai, aur uska pani aankh ke liye baaise shifa hai.'' Bukhari , Muslim . aur Sahih Muslim ki riwayat mein hai : ''wo (khanbi) us man mein se hai jo Allah Taala ne Musa (Alaihissalam) par nazil farmaya tha.'' muttafaq aleh."
4185,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Jaafar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko kakdi ke sath khajoor tanaawul farmatey huey dekha. muttafaq aleh."
4186,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham (Makka ke qarib) marruz-zohraan ke maqam par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath they, ham peelu chun rahey they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''in mein se siyah rang ki chuno kyonkey wo ziyada achhi hain.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se arz kiya gaya, kya aap bakriyan charaaya kartey they? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''haan, aur her Nabi ne bakriyan charaai hain.'' muttafaq aleh."
4187,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko akdoon bethey khajuren khatey huey dekha . eik dusri riwayat mein hai : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) un mein se jaldi jaldi kha rahey they. rawahu Muslim."
4188,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya koi aadmi apney sathi ki ijazat ke baghair do do khajuren eik sath na uthaey. muttafaq aleh."
4189,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jiskey ghar mein khajuren hon wo log bhookey nahin rehtey.'' eik dusri riwayat mein hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Aaisha ! wo ghar jis mein khajuren na hon to uskey rehney waley bhookey hain.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne do ya teen martaba farmaya. rawahu Muslim."
4190,"Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jo shakhs subah ke waqt saat ajwa khajuren kha ley to us roz uskey liye zahar baaise-nuqsan hai na jadu.'' muttafaq aleh."
4191,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aaliya ki ajwa (khajoor) mein shifa hai aur wo zahar ka tiryaaq hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
4192,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, ham par aisa mahina bhi aata hai ke ham is mein (choolhey mein) aag nahin jalaatey they, hamara khana sirf khajoor aur pani hota tha, albatta kahin se thoda sa gosht aa jata tha. muttafaq aleh."
4193,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki aal ne do din (musalsal) gehun ki roti sair ho kar nahin khai, un do (dino) mein se eik din khajoor hoti thi. muttafaq aleh."
4194,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki hayaate-mubaarka mein ham ne do siyah chizen (khajoor aur pani) pet bhar kar nahin khaeen . muttafaq aleh."
4195,"Hazrat Noman bin Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, kya tumharey paas tumhari chaahat ke mutabiq khaney peeney ki bahut ziyada chizen nahin hain? jabkey maine tumharey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aap ke paas pet bharney ke liye raddi qisam ki khajuren bhi nahin thin. rawahu Muslim."
4196,"Hazrat Abu-Ayub (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein khana pesh kiya jata to aap us se tanaawul farmatey aur us se jo bach jata wo merey liye bhej detey, eik roz aapney eik piyala meri taraf bheja jis mein se aapney kuchh nahin khaya tha, kyonkey is mein lehsun tha, maine aap se daryaft kiya, kya wo haram hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''nahin, lekin uski boo ki wajeh se main usey napasand karta hun.'' unhoney arz kiya, jis chiz ko aap napasand kartey hain, main bhi napasand karta hun. rawahu Muslim."
4197,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne (kachchaa) lehsun ya piyaz khaya ho wo ham se door rahey.'' ya farmaya : ''wo hamari masjid se door rahey, ya wo apney ghar mein betha rahey.'' aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas eik handiya laee gaee jis mein mukhtalif qisam ki sabziyan thin, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne is mein se boo mehsus ki aur farmaya : ''isey apney kisi sathi ke paas ley jaao.'' aur farmaya : ''khaao, kyonkey main us se ham kalam hota hun jis se tum ham kalam nahin hotey.'' muttafaq aleh."
4198,"Hazrat Miqdam bin Maadikarb (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apna anaj maap liya karo, tumhen is mein barkat ata ki jaeygi.'' Bukhari."
4199,"Hazrat Abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke jab dasterkhaan utha liya jata to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ye dua farmaya kartey they : ''her qism ki bahut ziyada pakizah aur ba-barkat hamd Allah ke liye hai, kifaayat ki gaee na chhodi gaee , aur na us se be-niyazi dikhai jaey, aey hamarey rab !'' Bukhari."
4200,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah taala bandey ke is tarze-amal se khush hota hai ke wo eik luqma khaye to is par uski hamd bayan karey ya wo koi chiz piye to is par uski hamd bayan karey.'' rawahu Muslim. (وَسَنَذْکْرْ حَدِیْثَنْی عَائِشَۃَ وَاَبِیْ ھُرَیْرَۃَ : مَا شَبعَ اٰلُ مُحَمَّدِ ، وَخَرَجَ النَّبِیُّ padhi. مِنَ الدُّنْیَا ، فِیْ بَابِ فَضْلِ الْفُقَرَآءِ اِنْ شَاءَ اللہُ تَعَالیٰ) ham Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadise : ''(ما شبع ال محمد) aur (خرج Nabi padhi. من الدنیا) Insha-Allah taala (باب فضل الفقراء) mein zikr karengey.''"
4201,"Hazrat Abu-Ayub (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas they ke khana pesh kiya gaya, maine koi khana nahin aisa dekha ke ham ne khaya ho aur uskey shuru mein bahut ziyada barkat ho aur uskey aakhir mein bahut kam barkat ho, ham ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! ye kaisey hua? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya :  jab ham ne khana khaya to ham ne is par Allah ka naam liya, phir koi aisa shakhs betha jisney Allah ka naam nahin liya us wajeh se shetan ne uskey sath khaya (is liye barkat uth gaee).'' (rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah)."
4202,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi khaye aur apney khaney par Allah ka naam lena bhool jaey to wo kahey : ''uska aaghaz aur ikhtitaam Allah ke naam se.'' rawahu Tirmizi aur Abu-Dawood."
4203,"Hazrat Umayya bin Makhshi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aadmi khana kha raha tha, usney Bismillah nahin padhi thi, yahan tak ke eik luqma baqi reh gaya aur wo luqma jab usney usey munh ki taraf uthaya to usney kaha : ''بسم اللہ اولہ و آخرہ'' to (ye sun kar) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) muskura diye , phir farmaya : ''shetan uskey sath khata raha yahan tak ke jab usney Allah ka naam liya to usney apney pet ka sab kuchh qai kar diya.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4204,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney khaney se farigh hotey to ye dua padha kartey they : ''her qism ki tareef Allah ke liye hai jisney hamein khilaya , pilaya aur hamein musalman banaya.'' rawahu Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood aur ibne-Maja."
4205,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''khana kha kar shukr karney wala, sabr karney waley roze-daar ki tarah hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
4206,Hazrat Imam ibne-Maja aur Imam Darmi ne Sanan bin San an Abih ki sanad se riwayat kiya hai. rawahu ibne-Maja aur Darmi.
4207,"Hazrat Abu-Ayub (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khana khatey ya koi chiz nosh farmatey to ye dua padhtey : ''her qism ki tareef Allah ke liye hai jisney khana khilaya , pilaya aur usey halaq se utarney wala banaya aur phir uskey nikalney ki raah banai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4208,"Hazrat Salman (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Taurat mein padha ke khaney ki barkat uskey baad haath munh dhoney mein hai, maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se iska zikr kiya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''khaney ki barkat us se pehley aur uskey baad haath munh dhoney mein hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi aur Abu-Dawood."
4209,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) baitul-khala (toilet) se bahar tashrif laye to aap ki khidmat mein khana pesh kiya gaya. Sahaba ne arz kiya, kya ham aap ki khidmat mein wuzu ka pani pesh na keren? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey wuzu ka hukm sirf us waqt diya gaya hai jab main Namaz padhney ka irada karun.'' rawahu Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood aur Nasai."
4210,Hazrat Imam ibne-Maja ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kiya hai. rawahu ibne-Maja.
4211,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu), Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke sareed ka piyala aap ki khidmat mein pesh kiya gaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''iskey kinaron se khaao aur iskey wast (beech) se na khaao kyonkey barkat wast (beech) mein nazil hoti hai.'' Tirmizi, ibne-Maja, Darmi. aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ''ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. aur Abu-Dawood ki riwayat mein hai farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi khana khaye to wo piyaley (plate) ke baalai (upri) hissey se na khaye balke wo uskey nichley hissey (yani apney aagey aur qarib) se khaye, kyonkey barkat uskey baalai (upri) hissey mein nazil hoti hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi, ibne-Maja aur Darmi."
4212,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko kabhi takiya laga kar khana khatey huey nahin dekha gaya aur na hi aap ke peechhey do aadmi chaltey huey dekhey gaey. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4213,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Haris bin Juz (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) masjid mein tashrif farma they ke aap ki khidmat mein roti aur gosht pesh kiya gaya to aapney khaya aur ham ne bhi aap ke sath khaya , phir aap khadey huey aur Namaz padhi. ham ne bhi aap ke sath Namaz padhi , aur ham ne is se ziyada kuchh nahin kiya ke ham ne kankariyon ke sath apney haath saaf kar liye. rawahu ibne-Maja."
4214,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein gosht ki dasti pesh ki gaee aur aap dasti ka gosht pasand farmaya kartey they, aapney daanton ke sath us se noch liya. rawahu Tirmizi aur ibne-Maja."
4215,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''chhuri ke sath (pakkey huey) gosht ko mat kaato kyonkey ye ajmiyon ka tariqa hai, balke usey daanton ke sath khaao, kyonkey aisa karna ziyada lazeez aur khaney mein ziyada Sehal hai.'' Abu-Dawud, Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan , aur dono ne farmaya : ye riwayat qawi nahin. (rawahu Abu-Dawood aur al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
4216,"Hazrat Umme-Munzir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartin hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) merey ghar tashrif laye aur Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bhi aap ke sath they, hamarey ghar mein khajoor ke khoshay latak rahey they, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unhen tanaawul farmaney lagey aur Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bhi aap ke sath khaney lagey , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya : ''Ali ! baaz raho, kyonkey tum abhi-abhi sehat-yaab huey ho.'' wo bayan karti hain, maine unke liye chukandar aur jau pakaey to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Ali ! ye khaao kyonkey ye tumharey liye ziyada munasib hai.'' rawahu Ahmed, Tirmizi aur ibne-Maja."
4217,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko bartan (handiya, degchi) ke paindey ke sath laga hua khana pasand tha. (rawahu Tirmizi aur al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
4218,"Hazrat Nabeesha (Raziallahu anhu), Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs kisi bartan mein kha kar usey achhi tarah saaf karta hai to wo bartan uskey liye maghfirat ki dua karta hai.'' Ahmed, Tirmizi, ibne-Maja , Darmi . aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Ahmed, Tirmizi, ibne-Maja aur Darmi."
4219,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ke haath par chiknaai lagi ho aur wo usey dhoey baghair so jaey phir koi chiz usey kaat ley to wo shakhs apney aap ko hi malamat karey.'' rawahu Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood aur ibne-Maja."
4220,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko roti aur hees (khajoor, paneer aur ghi) se tayyar shuda sareed bahut marghoob tha. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4221,"Hazrat Abu Usaid Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''zaitun ka tel khaao aur badan par lagaao kyonkey wo Mubarak darkht se hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi, ibne-Maja aur Darmi."
4222,"Hazrat Umme-Haani (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey ghar tashrif laye to farmaya : ''kya tumharey paas koi chiz hai? ''maine arz kiya, merey paas sirf khushk roti aur sirka hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ley aao, jis ghar mein sirka ho wo salan se khaali nahin hota.'' Tirmizi, aur farmaya : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
4223,"Hazrat Yusuf bin Abdullah bin Salam (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aapney jo ki roti ka tukda liya , is par khajoor rakhi aur farmaya : ''ye iska salan hai.'' phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne isey khaya (khaaya). rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4224,"Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main shadeed bimar ho gaya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) meri iyaadat ke liye tashrif laye, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apna daste-mubarak merey seeney par rakha jis se maine apney dil par uski thandak mehsus ki, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum to dil ke mareez ho, tum Haris bin Kalda Saqafi ke paas jaao kyonkey wo tabeeb (doctor) aadmi hai. wo Madina ki saat ajwa khajuren lekar unhen guthliyon samet koot daley, phir wo tujhey khila dey.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4225,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khajuron ke sath tarbooz khaya kartey they. Tirmizi . Imam Abu-Dawood ne ye izafa naqal kya hai : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmaya kartey they : '' uski haraarat uski thandak se kam ho jati aur uski thandak uski haraarat se kam ho jati hai.'' aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood .
4226,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein purani khajuren pesh ki gaeen to aap unhen cheer kar un mein se keedey nikalney lagey . (Hasan) rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4227,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ghazwa tabuk ke moqe par Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein paneer ka tukda pesh kya gaya, aapney chhuri mangaai, Allah ka naam liya aur usey kaata. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4228,"Hazrat Salman (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ghi, paneer aur rangey huey chamdey ke mutalliq puchha gaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ne jis chiz ko apni kitab mein halal qarar diya hai wo halal hai aur jisey apni kitab mein haram qarar diya hai wo haram hai, aur usney jis chiz ke mutalliq sukoot ikhtiyar kya to wo aisi chiz ke zimrey (catagory) mein hai jis se darguzar farmaya .'' ibne-Maja , Tirmizi . aur Imam Tirmizi (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : ye hadees gharib hai aur ziyada sahih ye hai ke ye riwayat moquf hai. rawahu ibne-Maja w Tirmizi ."
4229,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main chahta hun ke merey paas gehun ke safed aatey ki roti ho jo ghi aur doodh se goondh kar tayyar ki gaee ho '' Sahaba mein se eik aadmi utha aur wo usey bana kar aap ki khidmat mein ley aaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye ( ghi ( kis chiz mein tha ?'' usney arz kya : saandhey ki jild se baney huey bartan mein tha, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey ley jaao .'' Abu-Dawud, ibne-Maja , aur Abu-Dawood ne farmaya : ye hadees munkar hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood w ibne-Maja ."
4230,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kacha lehsun khaney se mana farmaya hai magar pakka hua ( khaney mein kuch harj nahin) rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood ."
4231,"Hazrat abu-Ziyad bayan kartey hain, Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se piyaz ke mutalliq puchha gaya to unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne jo aakhiri khana khaya is mein piyaz tha. rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4232,"Hazrat Basr ke dono beton se riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey paas tashrif laye to ham ne aap ke samney makkhan aur khajoor pesh kya. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) makkhan aur khajoor pasand farmaya kartey they. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4233,"Hazrat Ikrash bin Zuweb(Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, hamarey paas eik piyala laya gaya jis mein bahut sa sareed aur botiyan thin, main uskey atraaf mein haath  maar raha tha jabkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney samney se tanaawul farma rahey they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney baaeyn haath se mera daayan haath pakda, phir farmaya : ''Ikrash! eik jagah se khaao kyonkey khana eik hi tarah ka hai.'' phir hamarey paas eik Tabaaq laya gaya jis mein mukhtalif qism ki khajuren thin, main apney samney se khaney laga jabkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka haath purey Tabaaq mein ghoom raha tha, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Ikrash! jahan se chaho khaao kyonkey wo eik qism ki nahin hain.'' phir hamarey paas pani laya gaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney haath dhoey aur apney haathon ki nami apney chehrey, bazuon aur sar par mal li. aur farmaya : ''Ikrash! ye aag se paki hui chiz ka wuzu hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
4234,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke ehle-khana mein se kisi ko bukhar ho jata to aap jo ka Hurera bananey ka hukm farmatey, jab wo banaya jata to aap unhen hukm farmatey usey ghoont ghoont piyo, neez aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmaya kartey they : ''ye gham-zada shakhs ko quwat bakhshta hai aur mareez ke dil ko farhat bakhshta hai jis tarah tum mein se koi khatoon pani ke zariey apney chehrey se mel door karti hai.'' Tirmizi, aur farmaya : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
4235,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ajwa jannat se hai aur is mein zahar se shifa hai, aur khumbii man w salwa se hai, aur uska pani aankh ke liye baaise-shifa hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
4236,"Hazrat Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main eik raat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke yahan mehman tha aapney eik pehlu ( raan (ke mutalliq hukm farmaya to usey bhoona gaya, phir aapney chhuri li aur uskey sath us se merey liye kaatney lagey, itney mein Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) aap ko Namaz ke liye ittila deney aaye to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne chhuri phenk di aur farmaya : ''usey kya hua uskey haath khaak aalud hon.'' Mughira (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : meri munchhein lambi thin, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main miswak par rakh kar unhen kaat dun.'' ya farmaya : ''tum khud miswak par rakh kar unhen kaat lo.'' sanda rawahu Tirmizi ."
4237,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab ham Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath kisi khaney mein shareek hotey to ham khaney ke liye haath nahin badhaatey they jab tak Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) shuru nahin farmatey they aur aap apna haath badhaatey they, eik martaba ham aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath khaney mein shareek huey to eik bachi aai goya usey dhakela ja raha hai, usney khaney mein apna haath rakhna chaha to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey haath se pakad liya , phir eik dehati aaya wo bhi isi tarah tha jaisey usey dhakela ja raha ho aapney usey bhi haath se pakad liya , phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' shetan us khaney par , jis par Allah ka naam na liya jaey, dastaras hasil kar leta hai, wo us bachi ko lekar aaya taake wo uskey zariey dastaras hasil kar sakey, lekin maine usey haath se pakad liya , phir wo us dehati ko laya ta ke uskey zariey dastaras hasil kar sakey , lekin maine usey bhi haath se pakad liya , us zaat ki qism jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai ! be-shak us (shetan (ka haath , us ( bachi (ke haath ke sath merey haath mein hai.'' aur eik riwayat mein ye alfaz zayed hain : phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Allah ka naam liya aur khaya . rawahu Muslim ."
4238,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik ghulam khareedna chaha to aapney uskey samney khajuren rakhin, us ghulam ne bahut ziyada khajuren kha lein to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''be-shak ziyada khana be barkati hai.'' aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey wapis karney ka hukm farmaya. ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
4239,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' tumharey salan ka sardar namak hai.'' rawahu ibne-Maja ."
4240,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab khana laga diya jaey to apney jootey utaar diya karo, kyonkey ye tumharey paaon ke liye ziyada aaram deh hai.'' rawahu Darmi ."
4241,"Hazrat Asma binte-abi Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke jab unke paas sareed laya jata to aap ke kehney par usey dhank diya jata yahan tak ke uska josh haraarat khatam ho jata. aur wo farmati thin, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : '' aisa karna ziyada baais barkat hai.'' dono riwaayatein Imam Darmi ne naqal kin . rawahu Darmi ."
4242,"Hazrat Nabisha (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs kisi bartan mein kha kar usey achi tarah saaf karta hai to wo bartan uskey mutalliq kehta hai : Allah tumhen jahannam se azadi ata farmaai jis tarah tum ne mujhey shetan se azadi di.'' rawahu rizeen ."
4243,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Allah aur yome-aakhirat par eman rakhta hai wo apney mehman ki izzat karey. jo shakhs Allah aur yoam aakhirat par eman rakhta hai wo apney padosi ko takleef na pahunchaey aur jo shakhs Allah aur aakhirat key din par eman rakhta hai wo khair w bhalai ki baat karey warna khamosh rahey eik dusri riwayat mein : padosi ke bajaey ye alfaz hain : ''jo shakhs Allah aur aakhirat key din par eman rakhta hai wo sila rehmi karey.'' muttafaq aleh."
4244,"Hazrat abu-Shuraih al-Kaabi (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Allah aur aakhirat key din par eman rakhta hai wo apney mehman ki izzat karey aur wo eik din eik raat hai, aur ziyaafat teen din ke liye hai, uskey baad sadqa hai. aur mehman ke liye halal nahin ke wo mezban ke yahan itna qiyam karey ke wo usey tangi mein mubtala kar dey .'' muttafaq aleh."
4245,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se arz kya, aap hamen bhejtey hain, aur ham kisi qom ke yahan padaaw daltey hain to wo hamari mehman nawazi nahin kartey is barey mein Janab ka kya hukm hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar tum kisi qom ke yahan padaaw dalo aur wo mehman nawaazi ke mutabiq tumhari mehman nawaazi karen to usey qubul karo aur agar wo mehman nawaazi na karen to phir mehman nawaazi ka jo haq hai wo un se wasul kar saktey ho.'' muttafaq aleh."
4246,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, kisi roz ya kisi raat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ghar se bahar tashrif laye to aap ki abu-Bakar aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) se mulaqat ho gaee, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' us waqt tumhen kis chiz ne tumharey gharon se nikala ?'' unhoney arz kya, bhook ne , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' us zaat ki qism jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai ! mujhey bhi usi chiz ne nikala jisney tumhen nikala hai, chalo! ''wo aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath chal diye. aap eik Ansari sahabi ke paas tashrif laye lekin wo ghar par nahin they, jab uski ehliya ne aap ko dekha to kaha : khush aamadeed, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen farmaya : ''falan kahan hai?'' usney arz kya : wo hamarey liye mitha pani leney gaey hain, itney mein wo Ansari bhi tashrif ley aaye, unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur aap ke dono sathiyon ko dekha to pukar uthey : alhamdulillah, mehmani ke lihaz se aaj ka din merey liye bahut hi baaise-izzat hai, raawi bayan kartey hain, wo shakhs gaya aur khajuron ka khosha laya jis mein kachchi, paki aur umda her qism ki khajuren thin, usney arz kya, aap unhen tanaawul farmaeyn, aur khud usney chhuri pakad li , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey farmaya : '' doodh deney wali bakri se ehtiyat karna.'' usney unki khatir bakri zibeh ki, unhoney us bakri ka gosht khaya aur khajuren khaain aur pani piya. jab wo sair w sairab ho gaey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne abu-Bakar w umr (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya : '' us zaat ki qism jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai ! roze-qiyamat tum se un nematon ke barey mein sawal kya jaeyga, bhook ne tumhen tumharey gharon se nikala , phir tum un nematon se mustafeed ho kar wapis jaaogey .'' ( rawahu muslim) . ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees : '' ansaar mein se eik aadmi tha. . . . . (''baab alwalima'' ( mein zikr ki gaee hai."
4247,"Hazrat Miqdam bin Maadikarb (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : '' koi musalman kisi qom ke yahan mehman thehrey lekin wo ziyaafat key aq se mehroom rahey to uski nusrat karna her musalman par haq hai yahan tak ke wo uskey maal aur uski kheti se uska ziyaafat ka haq le-ley.'' Darmi, Abu-Dawood. aur Abu-Dawood ki riwayat mein hai : ''jo kisi qom ke yahan mehman thehra lekin unhoney uski ziyaafat na ki to wo apney haq ziyaafat ke barabar unke maal se ley sakta hai.'' rawahu Darmi w Abu-Dawood."
4248,"Hazrat abu-Ahwas Jushmi apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : maine arz kya : Allah ke Rasool! mujhey bataeyn ke agar main kisi shakhs ke paas se guzrun to wo meri ziyaafat na karey lekin uskey baad wo merey paas se guzrey to kya main uski ziyaafat karun ya usko badla dun (ke ziyaafat na karun )? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' balke ziyaafat karo.'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
4249,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ya unke ilawa kisi sahabi se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Saad bin Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) se ijazat talab ki aur farmaya : ''Assalamualaikum warahmatullah'' Saad (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya : w'alaikum Assalam warahmatullah, lekin unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki aawaz na sunai yahan tak ke aapney teen martaba salam kiya aur Saad (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi teen martaba salam ka jawab diya lekin aap ko na sunaya , jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) wapis tashrif ley gaey to Saad (Raziallahu anhu) , aap ke peechhey gaey aur arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! merey waliden aap par qurban hon, aapney jitni baar bhi salam kiya maine usey suna aur aap ko jawab arz kiya lekin maine aap ko (is liye) nahin sunaya ke main pasand karta tha ke aap se ziyada se ziyada salamti aur barkat hasil kar sakoon, phir wo ghar tashrif laye to unhoney aap ki khidmat mein Muaqqa pesh kiya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey khaya , jab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farigh huey to farmaya : ''neku-kaar tumhara khana khatey rahen, farishtey tum par rahmatein bhejein aur roze-daar tumharey yahan iftaar kartey rahen.'' (rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah)."
4250,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''momin aur eman ki misal us ghodey ke misl (jaisi) hai jo apney khuntey ke sath bandhaa hua hai daudta phirta hai lekin apney khuntey ki taraf hi lot aata hai, aur momin bhool jata hai (ghalati kar bethta hai) aur phir eman ki taraf palat aata hai, tum apna khana muttaqi logon ko khilaao aur mominon ke sath bhalai karo.'' (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
4251,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Basr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka eik bartan tha jisey chaar aadmi uthatey they, usey gharraa kaha jata tha, jab wo chaasht ka waqt honey par Namaze-chaasht padh letey to wo bartan laya jata aur is mein sareed tayyar kiya jata, phir Sahaba kiram uskey gird jama ho jatey , jab wo ziyada ho jatey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) do zaanu ho kar beth jatey , kisi Erabi (dehati) (dehaati) ne kaha : ye kis tarah bethna hai? Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ne mujhey narm salook karne wala sakhi banaya hai aur mujhey mutakabbir sarkash nahin banaya.'' phir farmaya : ''is (bartan) ke atraaf se khaao aur iskey wast (beech) ko chhod do is mein barkat ata ki jaeygi.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4252,"Hazrat Wahshi bin Harab apney baap se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Sahaba ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! ham khana khatey hain lekin sair nahin hotey , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''shayad ke tum alag alag khatey ho?'' unhoney arz kiya : ji haan ! aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum apna khana ijtimae shakal mein khaya karo, Allah ka naam liya karo (is tarah) is main tumharey liye barkat dal di jaeygi.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4253,"Hazrat Abu Usaib (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik raat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bahar tashrif laye merey paas se guzrey to mujhey aawaz di, main aap ki khidmat mein hazir hua , phir aap Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas se guzrey to unhen bhi aawaz di, wo bhi aap ki khidmat mein hazir huey . phir aap , umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas se guzrey to unhen bhi aawaz di, wo bhi aap ki khidmat mein hazir huey . aap chaltey gaey yahan tak ke kisi Ansari sahabi ke baagh mein tashrif ley gaey, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne baagh ke maalik se farmaya : ''hamen paki hui khajuren khilaao.'' wo eik khosha laye jisey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur aap ke sathiyon ne khaya , phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne thanda pani mangaayaa aur usey nosh farmaya , phir farmaya : ''roze-qiyamat tum se in nematon ke barey mein puchha jaeyga.'' raawi bayan kartey hain, umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne wo khosha pakad kar zamin par maara yahan tak ke wo khajuren Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke samney bikhar gaeen, phir arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! kya roze-qiyamat ham se inke mutalliq puchha jaeyga? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''haan , magar teen chizon ke mutalliq sawal nahin hoga, wo kapda jis se aadmi apna sattar dhaanptaa hai, ya roti ka tukda jis se wo apni bhook mitata hai, ya wo kamra jis mein wo garmi , sardi mein rihaaish rakhta hai.'' Ahmed, Behaqi ne Shobil-emaan mein isey mursal riwayat kiya hai. (rawahu Ahmed aur al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
4254,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab dasterkhaan laga diya jaey to dasterkhaan uthaey janey tak koi shakhs na uthey , aur jab tak khaney mein shareek tamam afrad farigh na ho jaeyn tab tak koi shakhs khaney se apna haath na rokey chahey (chaahe) wo sair ho jaey aur agar usey koi masla darpesh ho to uzr pesh kar dena chahiye, warna is tarah uskey sath waley ko sharmindagi hogi aur wo khaney ki zarurat ke bawajud apna haath rok lega.'' (rawahu ibne-Maja aur al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
4255,"Hazrat Jaafar bin Muhammad apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) logon ke sath khana khatey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sab se aakhir par khaney se farigh hotey they. Behaqi ne Shobil-emaan mein mursal riwayat kiya hai. (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
4256,"Hazrat Asma binte Yazid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein khana pesh kiya gaya to aapney wo hamein inayat farma diya, ham ne arz kiya, hamein khaney ki chaahat nahin, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' bhook aur jhoot jama na karo.'' rawahu ibne-Maja."
4257,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ikhattey khaya karo, alag alag mat khaao , kyonkey barkat jamaat ke sath hai.'' rawahu ibne-Maja."
4258,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aadmi ka paney mehman ke sath ghar ke darwazey tak jana masnoon hai.'' rawahu ibne-Maja."
4259,"Hazrat Imam Behaqi ne isey Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kiya hai, aur unhoney kaha : iski sanad mein zauf (kamzori) hai. (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
4260,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis ghar mein khana khilaya jaey is mein khair aur barkat us tezi se dakhil hoti hai, jis tezi ke sath chhuri oont ki kohan ko kaat'ti hai.'' rawahu ibne-Maja."
4261,"Hazrat Fajee Aamiri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur arz kiya, hamarey liye murda janwer ki kon si chiz halal hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tumhara kahna kya hai?'' ham ne arz kiya : ham Sham aur subah ke waqt doodh ka eik piyala peetey hain, Abu Nuaim ka bayan hai ke Aqba ne mujhey wazahat se bataya ke eik piyala subah , eik piyala Sham ko. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''merey baap ki qism ! ye to phir bhook hai.'' aapney us haal mein unke liye murdar ko halal qarar diya. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4262,"Hazrat Abu Waqid Laisee (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke kisi aadmi ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! ham aisi sarzameen par hotey hain jahan ham bhook ka shikar ho jatey hain to hamarey liye murdar khana Kab halal hota hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum subah ya Sham khaney ke liye koi tarkaari na paao, tab us haalat main tum murdar kha saktey ho.'' rawahu Darmi."
4263,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) peeney ke doran teen saans liya kartey they. Bukhari , Muslim . aur Imam Muslim (Raziallahu anhu) ne eik riwayat mein ye izafa naqal kiya hai : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmatey they : ''ye (teen saans lena) ziyada piyas bujhata hai, sehat ke liya  faaydemand hai aur ziyada baaise hazam hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
4264,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mishkeezey ke munh se peeney se mana farmaya hai. muttafaq aleh."
4265,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mishkeezon ke munh mod kar un se pani peeney se mana farmaya hai. aur eik riwayat mein izafa naqal kiya hai : mishkeezon ka munh modanaa ye hai ke uska dahaana ultaa-kar phir un se piya jaey. muttafaq aleh."
4266,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mana farmaya ke aadmi khada ho kar piye. rawahu Muslim."
4267,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se koi shakhs khada ho kar na piye, tum mein se jo shakhs bhool jaey to wo qai kar dey.'' rawahu Muslim."
4268,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine dol mein aabe-zam-zam Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pesh kiya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khadey ho kar nosh farmaya. muttafaq aleh."
4269,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney namaze-Zohar ada ki phir logon ke masayel hal karney ke liye wo koofa ke chabootrey par beth gaey yahan tak ke namaze-Asr ka waqt ho gaya, phir pani laya gaya to unhoney pani piya , apna chehraa aur haath dhoey , aur raawi ne zikr kiya, aapney apna sar aur dono paaon dhoey , phir khadey huey aur bacha hua pani khadey ho kar piya , phir farmaya : log khadey ho kar peena napasand kartey hain, jabkey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne isi tarah kiya jaisey maine kiya. Bukhari."
4270,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik Ansari sahabi ke paas tashrif ley gaey aur aap ke sath aap ke eik sathi bhi they, aapney salam kiya to us aadmi ne salam ka jawab diya jabkey aadmi baagh ko pani laga raha tha, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar terey paas raat ka baasi pani mishkeezey mein hai to theek warna ham taalaab se munh laga kar pi letey hain.'' us aadmi ne arz kiya, merey paas raat ka baasi pani hai, wo sayeban ki taraf gaya, piyaley mein pani dala phir is par ghar mein pali hui bakri ka doodh dhoya (aur usey aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pesh kiya) to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne nosh farmaya, wo aadmi dobara laya to us aadmi ne piya , jo ke aap ke sath tha. Bukhari."
4271,Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs chaandi ke bartan mein peeta hai to wo apney pet mein jahannam ki aag undeltaa hai.'' Bukhari Muslim . muttafaq aleh. aur Muslim ki riwayat mein hai : ''be-shak jo shakhs chaandi aur soney ke bartan mein khata aur peeta hai.''
4272,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''bareek aur mota reshmi kapda mat pahna karon aur soney chaandi ke bartan mein piyo aur na unki pleton mein khaao , kyonkey wo un (kafiron) ke liye duniya mein hain aur tumharey liye aakhirat mein hain.'' muttafaq aleh."
4273,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke liye ghar mein pali hui bakri ka doodh dhoya gaya aur phir uskey sath Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ke ghar ke kunwen ka pani milaya gaya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein wo piyala pesh kiya gaya to aapney usey nosh farmaya , aap ke baain taraf Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) they aur aap ke daain taraf eik Erabi (dehati) (dehaati) tha, umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! Abu-Bakar ko den , lekin aapney us Erabi (dehati) ko ata farmaya jo ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daain taraf tha, phir farmaya : ''daayan to daayan hi hai.'' eik riwayat mein hai : ''daeyn taraf walon ko, daain taraf walon ko , suno ! daain taraf walon ko muqaddam rakho.'' muttafaq aleh."
4274,"Hazrat Sehal bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat main eik piyala pesh kiya gaya to aapney us se nosh farmaya , aap ke daain taraf eik chhota sa ladka tha jabkey umr raseeda (buzurg) log aap ke baain taraf they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ladkey ! kya tum ijazat detey ho ke main ye piyala umr raseeda ashkhaas ko de-dun?'' usney kaha : Allah ke Rasool ! main aap ki bachi hui chiz apney ilawa kisi ko dena pasand nahin karta , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne wo usey hi ata farmaya. muttafaq aleh. ham Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees Insha-Allah-Taalaa (muajzaat ke baab) mein zikr karengey."
4275,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke ehad mein chaltey phirtey aur khadey ho kar bhi kha pi liya kartey they. Tirmizi, ibne-Maja , Darmi . aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi, ibne-Maja aur Darmi."
4276,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha, maine dekha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khadey ho kar bhi aur beth kar bhi pi liya kartey they. rawahu Tirmizi."
4277,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne bartan mein saans leney ya is mein phunk maarney se mana farmaya hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood aur ibne-Maja."
4278,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''oont ki tarah eik hi ghoont mein na piyo balke do aur teen ghoonton mein piyo aur jab tum piyo to Allah ka naam lo aur jab tum bartan munh se hataao to Alhamdu-lillah kaho.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
4279,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mashrub mein phunk maarney se mana farmaya to eik aadmi ne arz kiya, bartan mein gira hua tinkaa dekhun to phir (kya karun)? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey phenk do.'' usney arz kiya, main eik saans se sairab nahin hota, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apney munh se piyala hata, phir saans ley.'' rawahu Tirmizi aur Darmi."
4280,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne piyaley ke tootey huey hissey se peeney se aur mashrub mein phunk maarney se mana farmaya hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4281,"Hazrat Kabsha (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) merey paas tashrif laye to aapney latkey huey mishkeezey se khadey ho kar pani piya , maine us ( mishkeezey (ke munh ki taraf tawajjoh rakhi aur maine us (mishkeezey ke munh) ko kaat liya. Tirmizi, ibne-Maja. aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees Hasan gharib sahih hai. rawahu Tirmizi aur ibne-Maja."
4282,"Hazrat Imam Zohri ne Urwa ki sanad se Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat kiya hai, unhoney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko thanda sheereen mashrub ziyada pasand tha. Tirmizi aur unhoney kaha : sahih wo hai jo Zohri ki sanad se Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se mursal riwayat kiya gaya hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
4283,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi khana khaye to wo yun dua karey : ''aey Allah ! is mein barkat ata farma, aur hamein is se behtar khila.'' aur jab doodh piye to yun dua karey : ''aey Allah is mein barkat ata farma aur hamein is se ziyada ata farma.'' kyonkey doodh ke siwa koi aisi chiz nahin jo khaney se kifaayat karey.'' rawahu Tirmizi aur Abu-Dawood."
4284,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke liye saqiya se aabe-sheereen (meetha-paani) laya jata tha, mashhoor hai ke wo Madina se do roz ki masafat (doori) par eik chashma hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4285,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs soney ya chaandi ke bartan mein , ya kisi aisey bartan mein , jis mein us (soney ya chaandi) mein se kuchh ho to wo shahs apney pet mein jahannam ki aag hi undeltaa hai.'' rawahu Dar-Qutni."
4286,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine apney is piyaley mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko her qism ka mashrub pilaya , shehad , nabeez , pani aur doodh . rawahu Muslim."
4287,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke liye eik mishkeezey mein nabeez tayyar kiya karti thin, jisey ooper se baandh diya jata tha, aur uskey nichey bhi munh tha, ham subah nabeez tayyar kartin to aap usey Sham ko nosh farma letey aur ham Sham ko tayyar kartin to aap usey subah ko nosh farma letey they. rawahu Muslim."
4288,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke liye raat ke pehley hissey mein nabeez tayyar ki jati, jab us din subah hoti to aap usey nosh farmatey aur raat ko bhi peetey , agley din aur agli raat bhi nosh farmatey aur agley roz Asr tak nosh farma letey, agar kuchh bach jati aap usey khaadim ko pila detey ya phir aap ke hukm par usey undel diya jata. rawahu Muslim."
4289,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke liye mishkeezey mein nabeez tayyar ki jati thi, agar wo mishkeeza na paatey to phir aap ke liye patthar ke bartan mein nabeez tayyar ki jati thi. rawahu Muslim."
4290,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kadu ke banaey huey bartan, sabz (hara) ghadey, raughan kiye huey bartan aur lakdi se kuredey huey bartan mein nabeez tayyar karney se mana farmaya , aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne chamdey ke mishkeezon mein nabeez tayyar karney ka hukm farmaya. rawahu Muslim ."
4291,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maine tumhen (mazkura) bartanon (mein nabeez tayyar kerney) se mana kya tha, koi bartan na to kisi chiz ko halal karta hai aur na usey haram karta hai, her nasha aawar chiz haram hai.'' eik dusri riwayat mein hai, farmaya : ''maine chamdey ke bartanon ke ilawa deegar bartanon mein mashrubat (rakhney, peeney) se tumhen mana kya tha, tum tamam bartanon mein piyo, magar nasha aawar chizen mat piyo.'' rawahu Muslim ."
4292,Hazrat abu-Malik Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''meri ummat ke kuch log sharab ka koi aur naam rakh kar sharab noshi karengey.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood w ibne-Maja .
4293,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Ubai Aufi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne sabz (hara) ghadey ki nabeez se mana farmaya to maine arz kya, kya ham safed mein pi liya keren? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' nahin .'' Bukhari ."
4294,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab Suraj ghurub ho jaey ya jab tum Sham karo to apney bachon ko rok liya karo, kyonkey us waqt shetan phel jatey hain, lekin jab raat ki eik ghadi guzar jaey to un ( bachon ( ko chhod do aur darwazey band kar lo aur Allah ka naam lo , kyonkey shetan band darwaza nahin kholta, apney mishkeezey band rakho, un par Allah ka naam lo, apney bartan dhanp kar rakho un par Allah ka naam lo, chahey koi maamuli chiz hi un par rakho aur apney chiragh bujha diya karo.'' muttafaq aleh."
4295,"aur Bukhari ki riwayat mein hai, farmaya : '' bartan dhaanpo, mishkeezon ko baandho, darwazey band rakho aur Sham ke waqt apney bachon ko ikhatta kar lo kyonkey (us waqt ( jin phel jatey hain, aur uchak letey hain aur sotey waqt chiragh gul kar diya karo kyonkey kabhi-kabhi chuhiyaa chiragh ki batti khinch kar ley jati hai aur ghar walon ko jala daalti hai.'' Bukhari ."
4296,"aur Muslim ki riwayat mein hai, farmaya : ''bartan dhaanpo, mishkeezon ke munh baandho , darwazey band rakho , chiragh gul kar do, kyonkey shetan mishkeezey ka munh nahin kholta aur na band darwazey kholta hai aur na hi kisi bartan se dhakna uthata hai, aur agar tum mein se koi lakdi ke siwa koi chiz na paey to wo usey hi arz ke bal is par rakh dey aur Allah ka naam ley , wo aisey zarur karey, kyonkey chuhiyaa ghar ko ehle khana samet jala deti hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
4297,"aur Muslim hi ki riwayat mein hai, farmaya : ''jab Suraj ghurub ho jaey to raat ki ibtidaai (shuruati) taareeki ghayeb ho janey tak apney maweshi aur apney bachey na chhodo, kyonkey us waqt shetan chhodey jatey hain.'' rawahu Muslim."
4298,"aur Muslim hi ki riwayat mein hai, farmaya : '' bartan dhaanpo , mishkeezon ke munh baandho , kyonkey saal main eik aisi raat hai jis mein wabaa phailti hai, aur wo wabaa jab aisey bartan se guzarti hai jis par dhakna na ho ya kisi aisey mishkeezey se guzarti hai jis ka munh band na ho to wo is mein dakhil ho jati hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
4299,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, abu-Humaid Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) naqee se doodh ka bartan lekar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum ne usey dhanpa kyon nahin, chahey tum arz ke bal is par eik lakdi rakh letey .'' muttafaq aleh."
4300,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu), Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum sotey waqt apney gharon mein aag (ko jaltey huey ( mat chhodo.'' muttafaq aleh."
4301,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Madina mein raat ke waqt eik ghar ehle khana samet jal gaya, uskey mutalliq Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko bataya gaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye aag tumhari dushman hai, jab soney lago to usey bujha diya karo.'' muttafaq aleh."
4302,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jab tum raat ke waqt kutton ke bhonkne aur gadhon ke hengney ki aawaz suno to ( اَعُوْذُ بِاللہِ مِنَ الشَّیْطَانِ الرَّجِیْمِ ( padho , kyonkey wo aisi chizen dekhtey hain jo tum nahin dekhtey , jab (raat ke waqt ( logon ka aana-jaana khatam ho jaey to tum (gharon sey) nikalna kam karo, kyonkey Allah azz-w-jall raat ke waqt apni makhluq mein se jo chahta hai phela deta hai, aur darwazey band rakho aur un par Allah ka naam lo, kyonkey jab darwaza band kar diya jaey aur is par Allah ka naam liya jaey to shetan usey nahin kholta, bartan dhaanpo aur khaali bartan ulta karkey rakho aur mishkeezon ke munh band rakho.'' (rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah)."
4303,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik chuhiyaa batti khinchtey huey aai aur usey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke samney us chatai par rakh diya, jis par aap tashrif farma they, aur usney dirham barabar chatai jala di, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum soney lago to apney chiragh gul kar diya karo kyonkey shetan is tarah ki kisi chiz ki is tarah ke kaam par raahnumai karta hai to wo tumhen jala deta hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
